<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features</Paragraph>
<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>SeriesType to set the chart series type like pie,column,etc..</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>SeriesStroke to set the stroke and interior color</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>SeriesVisibility and effects to set the visible property</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>SeriesValue to set the value property of the series</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Series Type"</Bold> sets the type of the series. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The text box <Bold>"Label"</Bold> sets the Label of the series. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Interior"</Bold> sets the color for the interior of series. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Stroke"</Bold> sets the color for the series stroke. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The text box <Bold>"Stroke Thickness"</Bold> sets the thickness of the border of series. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Enable Effects"</Bold> sets the enable effects of series. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Is Rotated"</Bold> rotates the series. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Show Tooltip"</Bold> help to enable the visibility of tooltip of series. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"ColorEach"</Bold> check box allows enabling or disabling applying different colors to segments.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Palette"</Bold> combo box allows users to select built-in color palettes, which are used as interior colors for chart series segments.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"StrokePalette"</Bold> combo box allows users to select built-in color palettes, which are used as stroke colors for chart series segments.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

</List>


